Hi, someone can help me?
When download quote pdf from quote template, it's not look like to same as web version.
Is there any way to change in pdf design?
How to remove extra padding from pdf?
afaik you can’t, and it makes sense in the way that you want the on-screen pdf to be as close to the printed version as possible -> and most printers can’t do edge-to-edge printing
